tourBios.curYrHigh: Earned PGA TOUR Latinoamérica conditional status by finishing T15 at the Bogota, Colombia Q-School in January.
tourBios.personal: Graduated from Instituto Cumbres-Alpes (High School) in Queretaro in 2014... Has two brothers, Jaime and Sebastián, and a sister, Lucia... His biggest thrill in golf is playig with his dad... Cristiano Ronaldo is his favorite athlete outside of golf... Real Madrid is his favorite professional team... Would like to trade places for a day with Roy McIlroy... Instagram name is @pablorincong
